Commands Series:
1)	$ reboot
2)	Once booting press E and replace “rhgb quiet”	by “rb.break”
3)	$ mount -o rw,remount /sysroot/
4)	$ chroot /sysroot/
5)	$ passwd
6)	Enter new password
7)	$ touch / .autorelabel
8)	Twice $ exit
9)	Access the system as root	 with the new password.
